The Bunnyman Resurrection [2014]

Bunnyman 2 is a sequel to the horror movie, The Bunnyman Massacre. Its UK title is The Bunnyman Resurrection.[1] The plot revolves around a psychopath who dresses in a bunny suit and typically uses a chainsaw to murder people along with his family, reminiscent of Leatherface in The Texas Chainsaw Massacre series.
